Type: Package
Package: leafpeepr
Title: Prepare Raking Targets from Census Microdata
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexander",
           family = "Rossell Hayes",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alexander@rossellhayes.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9412-0457"))
Description: Prepare data for weighting with raking packages by
    creating weighting targets from census microdata. Also recodes values
    and collapses values into an "other" category in both census data and
    survey data.
